  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-lemon-and-crab-sauce-with-spinach-and-ricotta-ravioli/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and slice (don't chop!) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-lemon-and-crab-sauce-with-spinach-and-ricotta-ravioli/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced garlic</strong> and <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-lemon-and-crab-sauce-with-spinach-and-ricotta-ravioli/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, zest your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-lemon-and-crab-sauce-with-spinach-and-ricotta-ravioli/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>spinach & ricotta ravioli</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the ravioli for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Add the <strong>washed spinach </strong>and cook for a final 30 secs</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>spinach & ricotta ravioli </strong>and <strong>wilted spinach</strong>, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-lemon-and-crab-sauce-with-spinach-and-ricotta-ravioli/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the shallot and garlic have softened, add your <strong>crab meat</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the juice of <strong>half </strong>the <strong>lemon[s] </strong>to the pan with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until the crab is warmed through</p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon </strong>into 2 wedges per person</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-lemon-and-crab-sauce-with-spinach-and-ricotta-ravioli/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>drained spinach & ricotta ravioli </strong>and <strong>wilted spinach </strong>into the sauce and gently stir it together until the pasta is coated â€“ this is your <strong>chilli, lemon & crab sauce with spinach & ricotta ravioli</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/chilli-lemon-and-crab-sauce-with-spinach-and-ricotta-ravioli/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chilli, lemon & crab sauce with spinach & ricotta ravioli</strong> with the <strong>lemon wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
